data.description: This well maintained gem awaits you on almost half an acre in the heart of North Augusta! Immerse yourself in the charm of this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom brick home, boasting a great location. Step into a fresh and inviting atmosphere with freshly painted rooms and recently finished hardwood floors. The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances and gas range. Notable updates in 2019 include a new roof, new heating and air system, and all-new windows, ensuring both energy efficiency and contemporary aesthetics. The bathrooms have been tastefully upgraded, complementing the stylish appeal of the entire home. Enjoy the convenience of newer ceiling fans in every room, along with updated hardware and cabinets for a touch of luxury. The spacious laundry room has been redone, offering versatility as a large pantry area. Plumbing upgrades add to the list of recent improvements, providing peace of mind for years to come. Step outside to a huge backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. A single-car carport adds practicality to this wonderful property. Located in the heart of North Augusta, this home is not just a residence; it's a gateway to convenience. Proximity to downtown North Augusta and Augusta, restaurants, parks, walking trails, the river, bowling, baseball parks, I-20, and more makes this home a prime choice for those seeking a vibrant and accessible lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this move-in-ready haven your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the joy of living in the heart of North Augusta.
